<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Keukita - Kelola Keuangan Rumah Tangga via WhatsApp & Sheets</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Chart.js -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
        .chat-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 5px;
        }
        .chat-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #f1f1f1;
        }
        .chat-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-40 bg-white/85 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-200">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16 items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-200">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-wallet text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Keu<span class="text-emerald-600">Kita</span></span>
                        <span class="hidden sm:inline-block ml-2 text-xs bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-emerald-200 font-medium" id="sync-badge">Auto-Sync</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 mr-2 hidden md:inline">Status Integrasi:</span>
                    <span id="integration-status" class="flex items-center bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mr-1.5 animate-pulse"></span>
                        Simulasi Aktif
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6">
        
        <!-- Navigation Tabs -->
        <div class="flex border-b border-slate-200 mb-6 overflow-x-auto space-x-2 scrollbar-none">
            <button onclick="switchTab('dashboard')" id="tab-dashboard" class="tab-btn active px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold border-b-2 border-emerald-600 text-emerald-600 flex items-center space-x-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i>
                <span>Dasbor Keuangan</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('simulator')" id="tab-simulator" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 flex items-center space-x-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-lg text-emerald-500"></i>
                <span>WhatsApp Simulator</span>
                <span class="bg-red-500 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full animate-bounce">Uji</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('pembagian')" id="tab-pembagian" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 flex items-center space-x-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>
                <span>Atur Alokasi (Budget)</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('integrasi')" id="tab-integrasi" class="tab-btn px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 flex items-center space-x-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-nodes text-indigo-500"></i>
                <span>Hubungkan Google Sheets & WhatsApp</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Tab: Dashboard -->
        <div id="content-dashboard" class="tab-content block space-y-6">
            <!-- Top Alert Box for Quick Action -->
            <div id="alert-banner" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 text-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-md flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-white/20 rounded-xl">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Gunakan WhatsApp Simulator!</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-emerald-50 text-opacity-90">Simulasikan pengiriman pesan keuangan dari WhatsApp untuk langsung melihat update angka di bawah ini.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button onclick="switchTab('simulator')" class="bg-white text-emerald-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold shadow hover:bg-emerald-50 transition duration-150 self-start md:self-auto">
                    Coba Simulator <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Financial Cards Grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <!-- Total Balance Card -->
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Saldo Total</span>
                        <span class="p-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900" id="dash-balance">Rp0</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Pemasukan dikurangi Pengeluaran</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Total Income Card -->
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Pemasukan Bulan Ini</span>
                        <span class="p-2 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 rounded-xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-emerald-600" id="dash-income">Rp0</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1" id="dash-income-count">0 transaksi</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Total Expense Card -->
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Pengeluaran Bulan Ini</span>
                        <span class="p-2 bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 rounded-xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-long"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-rose-600" id="dash-expense">Rp0</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1" id="dash-expense-count">0 transaksi</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Savings Rate Card -->
                <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Rasio Tabungan</span>
                        <span class="p-2 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-piggy-bank"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-indigo-600" id="dash-savings-rate">0%</h3>
                        <div class="w-full bg-slate-100 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-2 overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="bg-indigo-600 h-full" id="dash-savings-bar" style="width: 0%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Allocations and Analytics -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Alokasi Anggaran (Budgeting Categories status) -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 lg:col-span-2 space-y-5">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">Alokasi Anggaran Aktif</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Status penggunaan dana sesuai aturan alokasi Anda</p>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="switchTab('pembagian')" class="text-xs text-emerald-600 hover:underline font-semibold flex items-center">
                            Atur Alokasi <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right ml-1"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4" id="allocation-progress-container">
                        <!-- Budgets progress bar dynamically generated here -->
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Visual Chart Breakdown -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">Rasio Pengeluaran</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4">Porsi pengeluaran berdasarkan kategori utama</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative flex-grow flex items-center justify-center py-4">
                        <canvas id="expenseChart" class="max-h-[220px] max-w-[220px]"></canvas>
                        <!-- Overlay when no expenses exist -->
                        <div id="chart-no-data" class="absolute inset-0 bg-white bg-opacity-95 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center hidden">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 mb-2">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column text-lg"></i>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Belum ada pengeluaran dicatat</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick Manual Input & Transaction History Grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Quick Manual Input Form -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-1">Catat Manual</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-5">Input transaksi cepat jika tidak melalui WhatsApp</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <form id="manual-transaction-form" onsubmit="handleManualSubmit(event)" class="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Tipe Transaksi</label>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                                <button type="button" onclick="setManualType('pemasukan')" id="btn-type-income" class="py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold border-2 border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center space-x-1.5 transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-down"></i>
                                    <span>Pemasukan</span>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" onclick="setManualType('pengeluaran')" id="btn-type-expense" class="py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-600 flex items-center justify-center space-x-1.5 transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-up"></i>
                                    <span>Pengeluaran</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="man-amount" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Nominal (Rp)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="man-amount" required placeholder="Contoh: 50000" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="man-desc" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Deskripsi / Keterangan</label>
                            <input type="text" id="man-desc" required placeholder="Contoh: Beli Beras 5Kg" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 text-sm">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="man-category" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Kategori Alokasi</label>
                            <select id="man-category" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 text-sm bg-white font-medium">
                                <!-- Dynamically populated based on allocations configured -->
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white py-3 rounded-xl font-bold transition flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-plus text-sm"></i>
                            <span>Simpan Transaksi</span>
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <!-- Transaction History List -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">Riwayat Catatan Keuangan</h3>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Mencakup input WhatsApp simulator & input manual</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex space-x-2">
                                <button onclick="clearAllTransactions()" class="text-xs bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 border border-rose-100 hover:bg-rose-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl font-semibold flex items-center">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can mr-1"></i> Hapus Semua
                                </button>
                                <button onclick="exportToCSV()" class="text-xs bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl font-semibold flex items-center">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-file-excel mr-1 text-emerald-600"></i> Ekspor CSV
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Table / List -->
                        <div class="overflow-y-auto max-h-[340px] pr-1 space-y-2" id="transaction-list-container">
                            <!-- Transactions populated here -->
                        </div>

                        <!-- Fallback empty state -->
                        <div id="transactions-empty-state" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center py-10 hidden">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 mb-3">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Belum ada transaksi</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Coba input via Simulator WA atau form manual.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tab: WhatsApp Simulator -->
        <div id="content-simulator" class="tab-content hidden space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
                <!-- Left instructions panel -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-emerald-600">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-3xl"></i>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Uji Robot WhatsApp Anda</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Di sebelah kanan adalah simulasi HP Anda yang terhubung dengan bot WhatsApp asisten keuangan rumah tangga. Ketik pesan di kolom chat untuk melakukan pencatatan instan.
                        </p>

                        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 space-y-3">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-800">Format Perintah Dukungan:</h4>
                            
                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded-xl text-xs space-y-2 text-slate-600">
                                <div class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">1. Format Singkat (Direkomendasikan):</div>
                                <div><code class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold">+ [nominal] [keterangan]</code></div>
                                <div class="text-slate-500">Contoh: <code class="bg-slate-200/50 px-1 rounded font-mono font-semibold">+ 2500000 Gaji Bulanan</code> (Masuk otomatis ke pembagian)</div>
                                <div class="mt-2"><code class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold">- [nominal] [keterangan]</code></div>
                                <div class="text-slate-500">Contoh: <code class="bg-slate-200/50 px-1 rounded font-mono font-semibold">- 45000 Beli Makan Siang</code> (Mengurangi budget kategori Kebutuhan)</div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded-xl text-xs space-y-2 text-slate-600">
                                <div class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">2. Format Kategori Spesifik:</div>
                                <div><code class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold">+ [nominal] [keterangan] #[nama_kategori]</code></div>
                                <div class="text-slate-500">Contoh: <code class="bg-slate-200/50 px-1 rounded font-mono font-semibold">+ 150000 THR #Keinginan</code></div>
                                <div class="mt-2"><code class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold">- [nominal] [keterangan] #[nama_kategori]</code></div>
                                <div class="text-slate-500">Contoh: <code class="bg-slate-200/50 px-1 rounded font-mono font-semibold">- 200000 Bioskop #Keinginan</code></div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 rounded-xl text-xs space-y-1 text-slate-600">
                                <div class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">3. Cek Status Alokasi via WA:</div>
                                <div>Ketik <code class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold">status</code> untuk melihat sisa saldo dan batas budget saat ini.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Direct quick template buttons -->
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider block">Ketuk Untuk Cepat Menguji</span>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                                <button onclick="simulateQuickMessage('+ 3500000 Gaji Bulanan')" class="bg-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs py-2 px-3 rounded-xl font-semibold border border-emerald-200 text-left truncate transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-money-bill-wave mr-1.5"></i> + 3.5jt Gaji
                                </button>
                                <button onclick="simulateQuickMessage('- 65000 Belanja Sayur')" class="bg-rose-50 hover:bg-rose-100 text-rose-800 text-xs py-2 px-3 rounded-xl font-semibold border border-rose-200 text-left truncate transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping mr-1.5"></i> - 65rb Belanja
                                </button>
                                <button onclick="simulateQuickMessage('- 120000 Beli Sepatu Baru #Keinginan')" class="bg-amber-50 hover:bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs py-2 px-3 rounded-xl font-semibold border border-amber-200 text-left truncate transition text-xs">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-shirt mr-1.5"></i> - 120rb Sepatu
                                </button>
                                <button onclick="simulateQuickMessage('status')" class="bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs py-2 px-3 rounded-xl font-semibold border border-blue-200 text-left truncate transition">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-list-check mr-1.5"></i> Cek Status WA
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Phone Simulator panel -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex justify-center">
                    <!-- Phone frame container -->
                    <div class="w-full max-w-[390px] h-[650px] bg-slate-900 rounded-[40px] p-3.5 shadow-2xl border-4 border-slate-800 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden">
                        
                        <!-- Top Camera Notch -->
                        <div class="absolute top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-full z-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-slate-800 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                            <span class="w-12 h-1 bg-slate-800 rounded-full"></span>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Screen Area -->
                        <div class="flex-grow bg-[#efeae2] rounded-[28px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col relative pt-8 pb-3">
                            
                            <!-- WhatsApp Header -->
                            <div class="bg-[#075e54] text-white px-4 py-2 flex items-center justify-between shadow-md">
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left text-sm cursor-pointer"></i>
                                    <div class="relative">
                                        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-sm border border-emerald-400">
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-400 border border-white rounded-full"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">KeuKita Bot 🤖</h4>
                                        <p class="text-[10px] text-emerald-100 opacity-90">Asisten Keuangan Online</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-sm text-emerald-100">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-video hover:text-white cursor-pointer"></i>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-phone hover:text-white cursor-pointer"></i>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-ellipsis-vertical hover:text-white cursor-pointer"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Chat Messages Scroll Container -->
                            <div id="chat-messages-container" class="flex-grow p-3 overflow-y-auto space-y-3 chat-scroll flex flex-col">
                                <!-- Initial Bot Greeting Message -->
                                <div class="max-w-[85%] self-start bg-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm text-xs text-slate-800 leading-relaxed border border-slate-100">
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-600 mb-1">KeuKita Bot 🤖</p>
                                    Halo! Saya asisten pencatatan keuangan Anda. Kirim format transaksi seperti:
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-1 space-y-0.5 text-slate-500">
                                        <li><code class="bg-slate-100 p-0.5 rounded font-semibold font-mono text-emerald-700">+ 1000000 Gaji</code></li>
                                        <li><code class="bg-slate-100 p-0.5 rounded font-semibold font-mono text-rose-700">- 20000 Beli Kopi</code></li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p class="mt-1.5 font-medium">Ketik <span class="font-bold underline text-slate-900">status</span> untuk cek dana!</p>
